NOTICE OF LIEN AFFIDAVIT
STATE OF TEXAS
COUNTY OF BEXAR
As of March 23, 2022:
The undersigned, of the County of Bexar and State of Texas, the legal and equitable owner of a certain continuing lien for payment of
maintenance assessments to the Las Ventanas at Crownridge Townhomes Owners' Association, Inc. , more fully described in the
Declaration of Covenants, Conditions & Restrictions, duly recorded in the Official Public Records of Real Property, Bexar County,
Texas, against the following property, to wit:
SUBJECT PROPERTY:
136 Avenue Ventana , San Antonio, TX 78256
LEGAL DESCRIPTION:
NCB 18333, BLK 8, LOT 22 (LAS VENTANAS
TOWNHOMES UT-1 PUD)
LAST KNOWN OWNER(S):
James Hunter and Amanda Hunter
AMOUNT OF ARREARAGE AT FILING:
CONTACT FOR AFFIDAVIT OF SATISFACTION:
$5,361.78
Crist Law Firm, PLLC
3123 N.W. Loop 410
San Antonio, Texas 78230
(210) 340-3277
Affidavit filed for period up to and including March 23, 2022. Please contact the Association for achil payout. yAmount due is subject
to the addition of interest, monthly accounting charges, and other fees and charges.
DATED: 23 March 2022
By:
WILLIAM D. CRIST
Attorney for the Las Ventanas at Crownridge
Townhomes Owners' Association, Inc.
STATE OF TEXAS
COUNTY OF BEXAR
This instrument was acknowledged before me on the March 23, 2022, by William D. Crist, attorney for the Las Ventanas at
Crownridge Townhomes Owners' Association, Inc.
CHRISTOPHER D. MERIDITH

Expires May 18, 2025
